        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK329">
<l>kolaiviṉaiya rākiya mākkaḷ pulaiviṉaiyar</l>
<l>puṉmai terivā rakattu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Men who destroy life are base men, in the estimation of those who know the nature of meanness.</l>
            </lg>
